'''Self-Regulating Droidmaker''' was a fully automated machine for converting raw materials into droids.

Based on the same principles as the [[Construction droid/Legends|construction droid]], the Droidmaker required no dedicated setup or manufacturing facilities. It was produced by the [[Loronar Corporation/Legends|Loronar Corporation]] shortly before the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]].

